      "date": "2018-05-21 04:18:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhat are the interop implications and abi implicatiosn here? People might have scripts and such expecting the old location.\n\nInterestingly I did some digging and it's not llite options that's misnamed. osc was named the same way too, but was then renamed without renaming the llite counterpart (check e.g. lustre/Changelog for a reference to old naming in osc).\n\nShould we install a symlink to keep the old name too?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
